Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:27.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:30.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Sweet love in love world
